FBIS4-16877 "drsov076_r_94008" FBIS-SOV-94-076 Daily Report 19 Apr 1994 Azerbaijan Bomb Found on Baku Train, 2 Suspects Detained Bomb Found on Baku Train, 2 Suspects Detained NC1904183094 Baku Azerbaycan Radio Televiziyasi Television Network in Azeri 1600 GMT 19 Apr 94 NC1904183094 Baku Azerbaycan Radio Televiziyasi Television Network Azeri BFN [Text] According to information provided by the National Security Ministry, a high-powered explosive device in a cardboard box was found and defused on the No. 5 Baku-to-Moscow passenger train during a joint search by the employees of the republic's National Security Ministry and the Interior Ministry at Baku train station some days ago. Two citizens suspected of the sabotage act were detained. The National Security Ministry's investigation department has instituted criminal proceedings and launched an investigation.
